snippet.title: Cloud Kingdoms gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Cloud Kingdoms, Dos PC game produced by Millennium Interactive in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/cloud-kingdoms/178/
Cloud Kingdoms is a great action/puzzle game. This game was created in '90 year. Each level is really peculiar and has its own strategies.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
